This paper deals with the problem of joint subcarrier and power allocation in a cellular downlink OFDMA system, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT), networking and communications (cs.NI), and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the optimization of a system utility function, which is related to machine learning (cs.MM) and optimization (cs.LG).
